column5: Leave Fri. for white river air. in white river. probaby a first. going with my wifes and my 5 kids. I say kids!!!! aged 41 to 52. makes me feel kind of old. been going to Ont on and off since 1964. with the kids for about 10 yrs now. still waiting 4 1 of them to get a monster pike. any way, wish us luck and a safe trip. thanks
Hey That You Tim Jias from Bay City If So have a Great time fishing this year Larry S
